\id PHP  
\h Philippi 
\toc1 Philippi Mite Henga Paul Lekhathot 
\toc2 Philippi 
\toc3 Philp 
\mt1 PHILIPPI  
\mt2 MITE HENGA  
\mt3 PAUL LEKHATHOT  
\is1 Kipa galjona malam non! Pathen toh kiguijopna hinkho lhum'a del jing  
\is1 Philippi Lekhabu sung thu umdan  
\ip Tahsan chate imatih chan'a kipana ding thudol Paul in ahilchen in ahi. Huhhingpu Jesu a kipana ineiyu hi koiman eilahpeh theilou diu ahi, ati. Hahsatna dinmun a jong kipana aumin, kineosahna jenga jong kipana aumin ahi; Jesu hetna hi kipana le phattheina ahin, lunglhaisel'a ilamlhah teng kipana eipeuve ti, hiche lekhabu sunga kon muchet ahi.  
\is1 Lekhathot jihpa chule ajih kum  
\ip Solchah Paul in AD 60-62 sunga ajih ahi. Hichu Rome lengvaipoa kon songkul atan laiya ajih ahi.  
\is1 Koi henga ajih ham?  
\ip Philippi mun'a tahsan chate dinga ajih ahin, hichu solam gamkai Greece ahi. Rome gamkaiya Philippi hi Europe pumpia dinga Solchah Paul in, Houbung aphudoh masatpen chu ahin, hichu AD 50 vel ahi. Philippi Houbung miten Paul kimanchahna ding cholam ahinthot jal uchun akipah lheh in, chule Paul in Houbung mite thuhil dihlouva kon akivenna diuvin ahilchah in, kipumkhat tah a hinkho aman jingna diuvin thupeh aneiye.  
\c 1  
\s1 Lemna Thu  
\p
\v 1 Hiche lekhathot hi Christa Jesu a sohchang Paul le Timothy a kon ahi. Keiman Philippi a um Pathen mitheng te ho Christa Jesu a um upaho le deacon ho jouse dinga kajih ahi.\x + \xo 1:1 \xt Act 16:12\x*  
\v 2 I-Pau Pathen le Pakai Jesu Christa chun lungset le cham-lungmon napeuhen.  
\v 3 Nangho kalunga kageldoh chanin ka Pathen ka thangvah jinge.  
\v 4 Keiman taona kaman seh le kipah thanom tah in nangho jouse dingin ka thumpeh jiuve.  
\v 5 Ajeh chu Christa Kipana Thupha hillhangna thudol'a, najah masat niuva pat tuni chan geiyin nangho katohkhompi nahi jing uve.  
\v 6 Chule keiman nanghoa natohpha tongpan'ah Pathen chun Christa Jesu ahungkit nikho lhin masangsea anatoh chu ajoma abulhit tei ding ahi, ti katahsan akichenin ahi.  
\v 7 Nangho na boncha uva thudol'a keiman lung hitia kagel hi adih ahi, ajeh chu nangho ka lungsunga kagelkhoh jing nahiuve. Hichea hi keima songkul lut thudol hihen chule Kipana Thupha lamdol a kihkonna thu kaseina hihen chule thutah a phudetna lam thudol hijongleh, nangho na boncha uva keima toh Pathen lungsetna kachan khompi nahiuve.  
\v 8 Ichan geiya nangho kangailut nahiuva chule Christa Jesu milungsetna a chu nangho na boncha uva kangai lheh u ahi chu Pathen'in ahenai.   
\s1 Alekhathot ho ataopehna  
\p
\v 9 Nanghoa ngailutna chu aha lonlhah cheh cheh a chule nangho hetna le hetkhenna a nakhantoube chehna ding uva katao ahi.  
\v 10 Ajeh chu keiman ipipen chu kiphamoa ham ti nang hon nahet diu kadeisah peh nahiuvin, hitia chu Christa ahungkit nikho hunglhun kahsea ngailutna theng le nolnabei hinkho naman theina dingu kati ahi.  
\v 11 Nangho huhhing nachan nau hi ga sona lama nadim jing uva, Jesu Christa a chonphatna na hinkho uva nasodoh theiyuva ahileh Pathen loupina le vahchoina hung hi ding ahi.  
\v 12 Chule kasopi te, nang hon ka hinkhoa ahung sohsaho chengse chu ipipen chu hita jongleh Kipana Thupha machal sahna dinga soh ahi tihi nahet dingu kadeiyin ahi.  
\v 13 Ajeh chu amitakip, hiche leng inpia umho eivesuiya pang sepai ho chan gei hin Christa jal a thihkhaova kihen kahi ti ahet sohkeiyu ahi.\x + \xo 1:13 \xt Act 28:30\x*  
\v 14 Chule keima songkul'a eikikoi jeh a hikom'a um atahsan jousen lungngamna le hansanna aneiyuva Pathen thu chu kichatna nei louva asei theiyu ahi.  
\v 15 Mi phabep ho chun Christa thu chu kimit thipna le midehnan aseiphongun, chule mi phabep hon lungdih pun aseiyuve, kiti ahi.  
\v 16 Amaho chun Kipana Thupha hongbit a panga kahi aheuvin, keima eingailut jeh uva aseiphongu ahi.  
\v 17 Midang ho vang chun Christa thu aseiphongu chu, chang phatchomna lunggel, lungdihpua hilou, thihkhaova kakihen hi bol genthei bea kaumna ding ngaitoa thusei phonga ahiuve.   
\s1 Paul lungsunga kipana  
\p
\v 18 Hinlah hichu imacha akhohpoi. Alunggon uchu dihlou hihen, adih hijongleh, Christa thu chu akiseiphong pou le kipah a kahi. Chule kipah jom nalai ding kahi.  
\v 19 Ajeh chu keima dinga natao u chule Jesu Christa Lhagao panpina chu, keima eikilhadohna hung hi ding ahi.  
\v 20 Ajeh chu keiman ginchatna le kinepna bulhingset kanei chu, keima jachatna a kachuh louhel ding, hinla keima Christa dinga masanga banga lung ngama kaum jom ding ahi. Chule ka hinkho hi hinna hihen, thina hijongleh Christa jabolna hung soh ding ahi ti katahsan e.   
\s1 Hin chu Christa, thi chu hamphatna  
\p
\v 21 Ajeh chu keima dinga hin kiti hi Christa dinga hin ahin, chule thi chu aphajo cheh ahi.  
\v 22 Hinlah tahsaa kahin le, keiman Christa dinga tohga phajo kaboldoh ding ahi. Hijeh chun hoijoh hi aphajo ham ti kahepoi.  
\v 23 Keima lung ngaichat ni neiya lunggel kichi-ah a uma kahi: Keima kache a Christa toh umkhom chu gamchenga keima dinga phajo'ah ahi.  
\v 24 Hinlah nangho khohsahna a tahsaa kahin jom ding hi kiphamo joa ahi.  
\v 25 Nangho jouse tahsanna a na khantou uva chule kipana a hetna nanei theina ding uvin, keima hing nalai ing ting nakithopi jom uvinge, ti ginchat hi kaneiyin kahen ahi.  
\v 26 Chule keima nangho henga avel'a kahung kit tengleh nang hon Christa Jesu a kiskonna naneibe chehna ding uva ka hinkhoa ipi aboldoh ham ti nahet dingu ahi.  
\v 27 Chukalvalin, nangho van gam mite chonin chon un, Christa Kipana Thupha to kitoh in hinkho mang uvin. Chuti chun keiman kahunga nangho kahung mu u hihen ahilouleh athua nachung thuu kajah tho hijongleh, nangho lhagao khat le lungkhat pua na dinkhom uva chule Kipana Thupha thua tahsan gal nasat u thudol chu henange.  
\v 28 Chule namelma teu kichatsahna a chun kicha hihbeh un. Hichu amaho kisuhmangna dinga amelchihna hung hi ding, hinla nangho vang Pathen Ama tah chun na huhdoh dingu photchetna ahi.  
\v 29 Ajeh chu nangho Christa tahsanna a chanpha seh changa nahi pouve, hinlah Ama jal a hahsatna jong thoh dinga chanpha changa nahiuve.  
\v 30 Hijeh chun masanga thoh gim puma kagalsat namu uvin, tujengin jong naja sohkeiyun ahi. \x + \xo 1:30 \xt Act 16:19-40\x*   
\c 2  
\s1 Christa akineosah chule choisanga aumna  
\p
\v 1 Hiti ahijeh chun Christaa hina jal a kitilkhouna um nam? Angailutna a konna lhamkonna um nam? Lhagaova kiloikhomna um nam? Lung nemna le kikhotona um nam?  
\v 2 Chuti ahileh nang hon nei kipasah tahbeh uvin, chuti chun lung pumpia thukhat kisauvin, khat in khat ngailu uvin, chule lunggel kithakhat neiyin chule doi kithakhat hiuvin.  
\v 3 Chang kilunggel bol hih in, midang pachat hol hih in. Kineosah in, nangma sanga midang chu aphajon gelin.  
\v 4 Na phatchomna ding bou velouvin, midang phatchomna ding jong ven.  
\v 5 Christa Jesun anei lunggel ngaito tobangma chu nang hon jong neiyuvin.  
\v 6 Ama Pathen ahi jeng vang'in, Pathen toh kibah a, kolchah den chu abolpoi.  
\v 7 Chusangin, Pathen ahina dinmun chu alhakangin, soh hina a kingainemna aneiyin chule mihem ahung kiso chun mihem pen ngaiyin ahung pengin,  
\v 8 Pathen seingaina jal'in Ama akineosah jengin chule thingpel'a migilou thina dinmun akilhen tai.  
\v 9 Hijeh chun, Pathen'in jabolna sangpen chan gei chun achoisangin chule min dang jouse lah a min chungnung pen chu Ama apeh ahitai.  
\v 10 Hitia chu Jesu min'a van mun'a, chule leiset chunga, chule leinoiya hijongleh khupnei jouse dilsu diu,\x + \xo 2:10 \xt Isa 45:23\x*  
\v 11 Chule paonei jousen Jesu Christa hi Pa Pathen loupina dinga Pakai tia aphondoh cheh dingu ahi.   
\s1 Vah tampi banga vannoiya vah ta ding  
\p
\v 12 Kangaitah te ho, keiman nangho kaumpi pet uva kahilnaho nangai bangu chun tu kaumlou pet dehset hin Pathen chu jana lentah le kichatna naneiyu photchetnan, huhhingna chu nahinkho uvah anatoh in sodoh un.  
\v 13 Ajeh chu Pathen nasung uva natonga chun alunglhaina tohdohna dinga ngaichatna le tohdoh theina tha napeuhen.  
\v 14 Nabol chasun'u chu phunchelna le nelkalna jaotha louvin bolun.  
\v 15 Hitia chu koima chan Pathen chate nahi nauva nalhep lhah louna dingun hiche khang gitlouna le vahkoi mite lah a vannoiya hinna vah chu vahdohsah un.\x + \xo 2:15 \xt Danbu Ni Na 32:5\x*  
\v 16 Hinna thu chu tuhchah un hitia chu Christa ahung niteng leh keima kilhaitetna a kajao hi mohjenseh a lhai kahilou, mohseh a tonggima kahilou chu kisonpia kanei theina ding ahi.  
\v 17 Hinlah keiman ka hinkho hi Pathen a dia kilhaina a twisun a kasunlhah ding hijongleh kipah ingting nanghoa tahsan umtah a Pathen a nakikatdoh tobangu hi ding ahi. Keiman hiche kipana chu chan neithei nahi cheh dingu kadei peh nahiuve.  
\v 18 Henge, nangho kipah unlang, keiman jong nakipa huvinge.   
\s1 Timothy le Epaphroditus  
\p
\v 19 Pakai Jesu lunglhaina ahileh Timothy hi nangho vila hinsol ding kati ahi. Chuteng chuleh nangho iti naumu aman eihil a kon'in kei dingin jong kisuhhalna hinte.  
\v 20 Ajeh chu nangho phatna ding lungdihpua lunggel ngaitona nei Timothy tobang nagel khoh diu kahe hih e.  
\v 21 Midang ho hin ama ama phattouna ding kigel khoh'ah ahiuvin Jesu Christa lam thu chu agelkhoh pouve.  
\v 22 Hinlah Timothy hin ama tah ahinan photchenna aneiyin, hiti hin chapa le apa tobangin Kipana Thupha seiphongna a keima toh tongkhom ahi ti nang hon naheuve.  
\v 23 Hilai mun'a kachung thu ipi aso aphotchetna aum tengleh ama nangho henga hinsol ding kati ahi.  
\v 24 Chule Pakaiya kakiskonna chu nangho to kimuto vah ding hi kakineme.  
\v 25 Tutadia dingin Epaphroditus naheng uva hinsol ding kangaito ahi. Ama hi sopi dihtah tohkhompi ahi.  
\v 26 Aman na munom lheh jeng uvin naheng uva kahinsol e. Chule ana dammo thudol najah uchu phamo asa lheh jenge.  
\v 27 Tahbeh in ama ana dammon chule thidehchet anahi'e. Hinla Pathen mikhotona chu achangin chule keima eikhoto dehset ahi. Ajeh chu keima lungkhamna chung chona lungkhamna kaneibe louna ding hiya ahi.  
\v 28 Hijeh a chu ama nangho kom'a hinsol ding kagel khoh ahi. Ajeh chu nang hon ama namu tengu leh nakipa uva chule nangho kalung olmopeh tahlouna ding ahiye.  
\v 29 Christian kingailutna chun kipah thanom tah in ama ana lem uvin chule hitobang mihi jabolna nei chu thilpha ahi.  
\v 30 Ajeh iham itileh Christa natohna a ahinkho ahahsatna ato ahi. Chule nang hon mun gamla tah a konna nabol theilou diu jeh a nangho thalhenga keima dinga aman eibolpeh ahi.   
\c 3  
\s1 Adihtah photchetna  
\p
\v 1 Kasopi ngaitah te ho, ipi chu hita jongleh Pakaiya kipah thanom'un. Hitiho sei ding hi kachimpoi, chule hiche hi na tahsan u honbitna ding ahijoi.  
\v 2 Chuche uicha ho lah a chun chingtheiyun–kihongpha uvin, hitobang miho chun thilse abolun, hitobang miho chun huhhing channa dinga chep natan diu ahi atiuve.  
\v 3 Ajeh iham itileh eiho Pathen Lhagaova kona Pathen hou cheptan tahbeh ihiuvin, Jesu Christa natoh chaisa a chu kingamdet a, tahsalama kiskonna neilou ihiuve.  
\v 4 Keima tahsalam boltheina jeh a kisong jeng jonglehng kisong thei kahi. Tahbeh mongin midangin tahsa lama kiskonna anei thei le keiman kison cheh theina kaneiye.  
\v 5 Keima ni-get nia cheptan kahin, Israel mihina pen-gui chu kaneiyin, chule Benjamin phunga kon Hebrew mi atahbeh chu kahi. Juda te Dan juina lama hakattah Pharisee ho lah a mi kahi;\x + \xo 3:5 \xt Rm 11:1; \xt Act 23:6; 26:5\x*  
\v 6 Keima katom ngai behseh jeh in houbung chu hoise tah in kana gimbol in, chule chonphat lamdol a keima danthua nolnabeiya jui bukima kahi.\x + \xo 3:6 \xt Act 8:3; 22:4; 26:9-11\x*  
\v 7 Keiman hiche ho hi atila chu manlutah a kana ngaisang anahi, hinlah tun keiman Christan anatoh chaisa jal'in hiho chu mohseh in kageltai.  
\v 8 Christa Jesu chu Pakai ahi tia kahet a pat in hiho jouse chu panna bei bep in kagel tai. Keiman Christa chu kaphatchompi theina dinga thil adang jouse chu nen kikholkhom tobang bep a kangaitoa kanungsun ahitai.  
\v 9 Danthu juina a keima chonphatna chu hitalouva Ama toh thakhat kahia hitia chu keima Christa tahsan jal a chonpha eikisima ahitai. Ajeh chu tahsan jal'a Pathen'in eiho chonpha a eisemu ahitai.  
\v 10 Keiman Christa chu kahet nomin, agimthohna chu thoh khoma, athina chu chankhompi kahi theina ding chule Ama thinaa konna kaithoupa thahat thilbol theina chu kachan theina ding kati ahi.  
\v 11 Hitia chu ipi iti jongleh keiman thinaa konna thokitna chu kachan tei ding ahi.   
\s1 Abidoi lam kat jing ding  
\p
\v 12 Keiman hiche ho chu kaneitai kati ahipoi, ahilouleh keima chamkimna chu chang kahitai katipoi. Hinlah keima Christa Jesun einei banga hi keiman jong hiche chamkimna chu kaneina tei ding kadel ahi.  
\v 13 Kasopi te ho, keiman hichu kanei hih laiye, hinla hiche thil khat bou hi kagut ahi. Keiman achesa thil chu kasumilin, kamasanga ipi um ham ti kagel khoh in ahi.  
\v 14 Keiman kilhaitetna chu achaina geiya lhai lhunga chule Pathen'in Christa Jesu a eikou nau van kipaman sanna ding mun chu hadel'a del kahi.  
\v 15 Lhagaova apilhing chengsen hiche hoa hin kinoptou hite. Ipiham jeh a lungkim louna nei aum le, hijong chu Pathen'in na seichet peh tauvinte.  
\v 16 Hinlah eihon imaskonnau chan geiya hi ituhchah diu angaiye.  
\v 17 Sopi deitahte ho, keima umchan tobang hin nangho jong um uvin, chule keima ho nung juiya pangho um chan'a kon'in kihil uvin.\x + \xo 3:17 \xt 1 Crth 4:16; 11:1\x*  
\v 18 Ijeh inem itileh masanga kana seipeh matchet jiu bangun chule tua jong kamit a kamitlhi puma ka seipeh u ahi, amaho chu achonna u chun Christa Thingpel melmaho ahiuve ti aphotchen u ahi.  
\v 19 Amaho chun mahthahna lam amano uve. Amaho atumpiu chu a pathen'u ahi, Akithang-at nau chu jachat akimun'a diu, amaho chun tu hinkhoa ding bou agelu ahi.  
\v 20 Ahinlah eiho Pakai Jesu Christa chenna van gam mite ihiuve. Chule eiho huhhingpu ahungkitna ding chu kinem'a ngah jinga ihiuve.  
\v 21 Aman itahsau thi thei hi alah a, Amaa banga loupina vouphea akhel ding, Aman thil ijakai athuneina thunoiya akoi banga athua ahin nunsah ding ahi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Pakaiya kipah thanom un  
\p
\v 1 Hijeh chun kasopi deitahte ho, Pakaiyah umdet jingun. Kasopi deitahte ho keiman nangho kangailu uvin chule kamunom uve, ajeh chu nangho hi kakipana le kanatohna ka lallukhuh nahiuve.  
\v 2 Tun keiman Euodia le Syntyche hengah, Pakaiya nahi lhon jeh in nakitomona lhon chu umsah lhon tahih in tia kangeh lhon nahi.  
\v 3 Chule nangma katohkhompi dihtah, nangman hiche numei teni hi kithopin, ajeh chu amani hi midang Kipana Thupha seiphong pehnaa gunchutah a pang lhon'ah ahi. Amani hi Clement to chule Hinna Lekhabua amin kisun dang hoto tongkhom'a ahiuve.  
\v 4 Pakaiya kipahtah in um jingun. Avel'in tikit inge–Kipahtah in um jingun.  
\v 5 Amitakip in naum nauva nabol jouseuva lunggel toh them nahiu hehen. Pakai hungloi tading ahi geldoh un.  
\v 6 Imacha lung olmona neihih un, chusangin, imalam jousea dingin taovun. Na ngaichat chu Pathen henga seiyun, chule athil boldohsaho jal in thangvahna peuvin.  
\v 7 Chuti henlang hileh Pathen a cham-lungmon konna, ijakai hetna a khel sohkeiya chun, nalungu le nalungthimu Christa Jesu a nahi jal uva chu napeh dingu ahi.   
\s1 Thil hicheng hi gel un  
\p
\v 8 Chule tun, kasopi deitahte ho, achaina keiyin-akitah lam, ja-umdol lam, adihlam, athenglam, lungset um le pachat umlam, aphalam le pachat thei lama auma ahileh hitiho hi lunggel un.  
\v 9 Nanghon keiya kon a nakihilsa hou, na sansa ho-u chule keima a kon a najahsa hou le namusa hou nitin in juiyun. Chuteng cham-lungmon Pathen chun naumpi dingu ahi.   
\s1 Philippi mite  
\p
\v 10 Nanghon keima nei gelkhoh kitnau jeh a Pakai iti kavahchoi hitam! Nanghon keima neigelkhoh jing uve ti kahei, hinla nang hon chutia kithopina thei phat kijen namulouvu ahi.  
\v 11 Hichu kangaichat umjeh a kasei ahipoi, ajeh chu keiman kanei khama chu lung lhaiya umje kahet ahi.  
\v 12 Keiman imacha nei louva um ahilouleh ijakai neiya umje kahen ahi. Itobang phat hunglhung dinga jong, oivaset ahilouleh keltah a umje jong chule ninglhingset hihen lhomcha hijongleh hiche thuguh chu kahet ahitai.  
\v 13 Ajeh chu keima thahat eipea Christa jal a chu ijakai bolthei kahi.  
\v 14 Hitima chun, nang hon tupet kahahsatna a nei panhu uhi nabol phalheh jeng uve.  
\v 15 Philippia a um nang hon naheng uva Kipana Thupha kahin pohpeh uva chu, nahetma bang uvin, sum le paiya eikithopia nangho bou nahiuvin chule Macedonia a konna kaga kholjin patkit chun koima houbung in achutibol pouvin ahi.  
\v 16 \x + \xo 4:16 \xt 2 Crth 11:9\x*Thessalonica kho a kaumpet jengin jong kithopina khatvei seh hilouvin avel in neihin thot uvin ahi.\x + \xo 4:16 \xt Act 17:1\x*  
\v 17 Keiman hiche kasei hi nanghoa thilpeh chu ka ngaichat ahipoi. Chusangin, lungset them nahijal uva kipaman nasan diu chu kadei joh ahi.  
\v 18 Tupet in ka ngaichat jouse kaneiye-chukalval in Epaphroditus khut a na thilpeh u chun ninglhingset in einei sah e. Hiche ho chu kilhaina gimnamtui kihal Pathen a dinga santhei le lunglhai umtah ahi.\x + \xo 4:18 \xt Potdohbu 29:18\x*  
\v 19 Chule hiche Pathen, keima eigelkhohpeh a chun, aloupinaa Christa Jesu a ahao dungjuijin na ngaichat jouseu chu pebukim nauvin nate.  
\v 20 Tun I-Pau Pathen'a chun loupina jouse atonsot atonsot in um jing hen! Amen.   
\s1 Achaina temna  
\p
\v 21 Pathen mitheng te jouse, Christa Jesu a hiho jouse chu keima a kon'in salam anape uvin. Sopite kaumpi chengsen salam nahin peuvin ahi.  
\v 22 Chule Pathen mitheng te adang dang ho jousen salam nahin thot uve, adehset in Caesar insung mitea kon'in salam napeuve.   
\p
\v 23 Pakai Jesu Christa lungsetna chun nalhagaovu umpi hen.   